&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Segoe UI'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 1:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Una vez dispuesto el circuito del esquema de la izquierda, se varía la tensión de la fuente a la entrada hasta obtener a la salida del regulador la tensión nominal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 2: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Se toman varias mediciones de la tensión de salida.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 3:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Se conecta una carga resistiva pura a la salida del regulador tal que circule una corriente determinada.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 4: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Se varía el valor de la carga hasta obtener a la salida la corriente de ensayo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 5:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Se toman nuevamente mediciones repetidas del valor de tensión a la salida.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 6: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Reducir el valor de tensión de la fuente hasta 0 V. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 7:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Con las mediciones efectuadas y los datos caracteristicos de los instrumentos se calcula el efecto de carga con su incertidumbre asociada.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:704;&quot;&gt;PASO 8: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Se verifica que el valor obtenido este comprendido dentro del dato garantizado en la especificación del fabricante.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
             </property>
            </widget>
           </item>
          </layout>
         </widget>
        </item>
